<view class="page survey-page"><view class="card survey-header"><view class="survey-title">今日康养指标</view><view class="survey-sub"> 通过几个简单问题，记录您今天的症状、睡眠、用药、运动与饮食等康养指标情况。 填写约 2–3 分钟，由您或家属代填即可。 </view><view class="survey-progress"><view class="survey-progress-bar"><view class="survey-progress-inner" style="{{'width:' + a}}"></view></view><view class="survey-step">第 {{b}} / {{c}} 步</view></view></view><view wx:if="{{d}}" class="card"><view wx:for="{{e}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="L" class="q-card"><view class="q-title">{{item.a}}. {{item.b}} <text wx:if="{{item.c}}" class="q-required">*</text></view><view wx:if="{{item.d}}" class="q-desc">{{item.e}}</view><view wx:if="{{item.f}}" class="q-options"><view wx:for="{{item.g}}" wx:for-item="opt" wx:key="e" class="{{opt.b}}" data-field="{{item.h}}" data-value="{{opt.c}}" bindtap="{{opt.d}}"><view class="q-option-text">{{opt.a}}</view></view></view><view wx:elif="{{item.i}}" class="star-wrap"><view class="star-row"><text wx:for="{{item.j}}" wx:for-item="n" wx:key="a" class="{{n.b}}" data-field="{{item.k}}" data-value="{{n.c}}" bindtap="{{n.d}}">★</text><text class="star-score">{{item.l}}/{{item.m}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{item.n}}" class="star-labels"><text class="star-label-left">{{item.o}}</text><text class="star-label-right">{{item.p}}</text></view></view><view wx:elif="{{item.q}}" class="score-wrap"><view class="score-head"><text class="score-val">{{item.r}}</text><text wx:if="{{item.s}}" class="score-unit">{{item.t}}</text></view><slider class="score-slider" min="{{item.v}}" max="{{item.w}}" step="{{item.x}}" value="{{item.y}}" data-field="{{item.z}}" bindchange="{{item.A}}"/><view class="score-range"><text class="score-left">{{item.B}}</text><text class="score-right">{{item.C}}</text></view></view><view wx:elif="{{item.D}}" class="text-wrap"><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="q-textarea" placeholder="{{item.E}}" value="{{item.F}}" maxlength="{{item.G}}" auto-height data-field="{{item.H}}" bindinput="{{item.I}}"></textarea></block><view class="text-count">{{item.J}}/{{item.K}}</view></view></view></view><view wx:else class="card"><view class="empty">加载中…</view></view><view class="card bottom-card"><view class="bottom-row"><button class="btn-secondary" bindtap="{{f}}" disabled="{{g}}">上一步</button><button wx:if="{{h}}" class="btn-primary" bindtap="{{i}}">下一步</button><button wx:elif="{{j}}" class="btn-primary" bindtap="{{k}}">提交指标</button></view><view class="bottom-tip"> 本问卷仅用于慢病随访与中医健康管理，不作为诊断依据。 若出现胸痛、明显呼吸困难、意识不清等严重不适，请立即就医或拨打急救电话。 </view></view></view>